author: Jorge Alonso
title: Leaked Video Shows The ‘Cash Me Outside’ Girl Getting Beat By Her Mother
text:
Tonight a video of 13-year-old girl Danielle Bregoli aka the “Cash me outside girl” getting beat by her mother started making the rounds on the Internet. 
Bregoli grew to fame earlier in the year after video of her appearance on the Dr. Phil, where she was openly disrespectful to her mother went viral. 

I’m not entirely sure how this video made it’s way onto the net but it’s pretty clear that someone needs to step in to take control of this situation because both the mother and the daughter are out of control.
